Date: Sun, 10 May 2026 18:58:36 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 6.12 5/5] mctp: driver: net: Fix MCTP over USB

Add fixes for MCTP over USB (option MCTP_TRANSPORT_USB).

Signed-off-by: Vadim Pasternak <vadimp@nvidia.com>
